Ezentis Gets EU20 Million Refinancing for Clean-Energy Projects

-- B y   T o d d   W h i t e
-- 
2011-08-31T16:32:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/ezentis-gets-eu20-million-refinancing-for-clean-energy-projects.html
Grupo Ezentis SA (EZE)  refinanced 20
million euros of loans for a 20-year term to underpin its
photovoltaic businesses, the Seville, Spain-based
telecommunications and construction company said today in a
filing.  Separately, the company obtained a 2.3 million-euro loan to
continue developing the renewable-energy ventures, it said. The
refinancing was made “at market rates,” Ezentis said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Todd White at 
 twhite2@bloomberg.net  